推奨項目(やんばるエリア): I will recommend for its rich natural environment and peaceful atmosphere. The lush forests, clear rivers, and rare wildlife offer a side of Okinawa that feels untouched and deeply calming. Compared to more developed areas, Yanbaru is quiet and less crowded, allowing visitors to experience nature and local culture at a relaxed pace. It’s an ideal place for people who want to enjoy authentic Okinawan scenery, wildlife, and a slower way of life. Also i would recommend them going to Neo Park definitely. The experience of feeding animals here is different
改善点の内容(やんばるエリア): No improvement is needed. I’m still learning the Japanese language, and since my girlfriend is a local from Saitama, it has helped me a lot when conversing with others.
